                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-21-victim221 t18030914-21-viclabel131"></join> at Bow; the prisoner was my servant; I sent him out with a barrow of bread on the 22d of August, value 30s. he never returned, or brought any money; the barrow, with two loaves, was brought back by a stranger.</p>
